# GRAPHICS::CASCADE_SHADOWS_CLEAR_SHADOW_SAMPLE_TYPE

## Summary
Call this to clear the cascade shadows sampling type, as previously set by CASCADE_SHADOWS_SET_SHADOW_SAMPLE_TYPE
